sequenceDiagram
    participant App as Your Application
    participant DV as Dataverse
    participant Storage as Azure Storage

    Note over DV: Export job created<br/>(manually via UI or by automatic scheduling)
    Note over DV: Job processes asynchronously

    loop Poll for completion
        App->>DV: Query job status
        Note over App,DV: Query msdyn_scpexportdatajobruns
        DV-->>App: Job status
    end

    Note over DV: Export completed

    App->>DV: Call msdyn_scpgetexportoutputfileurl
    DV-->>App: SAS URL (valid 120 min)

    App->>Storage: Download CSV file
    Storage-->>App: CSV data